 \int_{- \pi}^{0} \frac{z}{a-e^{-ix}} \ dx + \int_{0}^{\pi} \frac{x}{a-e^{-ix}} \ dx + i \int_{0}^{\infty}f(\pi + i t) \ dt + \lim_{R \to \infty} \int_{-\pi}^{\pi} f(t + iR) \ dt 
